### Create plan
POST http://localhost:8080/api/plans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Plano Mensal",
  "monthlyAmount": 99.90,
  "frequency": 1
}

###

### List all plans
GET http://localhost:8080/api/plans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get plan by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/plans/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update plan
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/plans/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Plano Mensal Atualizado",
  "monthlyAmount": 109.90,
  "frequency": 1
}

###

### Delete plan
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/plans/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
